{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so this plebiscite was, was scheduled to take place on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we young people, and we young students were-- and we were all so patriotic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we would walk down the streets and would call out, Osterreich, Osterreich!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on the other side of the street, all very well-organized, on the other side of the street, an equally large group would walk down and say, Heil, Hitler!",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Heil, Hitler!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Osterreich!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Heil, Hitler!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Osterreich!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I don't have to tell you which side of the street I was on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Friday night that week, before the Sunday, a group of us young people were going to get together and, and, and spend a pleasant evening together and meet at 7:00 or 7:30.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So around 6 o'clock, one of my girlfriends-- with whom I would have traveled together on the trolley but she lived in my neighborhood so we were going to go together to where we were supposed to meet in a restaurant-- called me and said, are you listening to the radio?",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think we are going to go out tonight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And why shouldn't we go out tonight?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, listen to the radio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, Hitler was at the far western end of Austria, you know, Tyrol, which borders on Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at 7 o'clock, Schuschnigg came on the radio and said, to avoid bloodshed, I have ordered not to resist the German invasion, or whatever he called it, which it was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we never did get to meet at that restaurant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was-- then Hitler had his triumphal progression from one end of Austria until he got to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There never was a plebiscite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and that, that was that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
